azine.com/articles/view/review-tesla-world-light\">\"Review: 'The Tesla World Light' \u2013 Point of View Magazine\"</a>. <i>POV Magazine</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-05-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=POV+Magazine&amp;rft.atitle=Review%3A+%E2%80%98The+Tesla+World+Light%E2%80%99+%E2%80%93+Point+of+View+Magazine&amp;rft.aulast=Mullen&amp;rft.aufirst=Patrick&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fpovmagazine.com%2Farticles%2Fview%2Freview-tesla-world-light&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Tesla+World+Light\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Thrill-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Thrill_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Thrill_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Thrill, Scott (23 May 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cartoonbrew.com/interviews/hard-utopian-matthew-rankin-new-film-tesla-world-light-150984.html\">\"It's Hard to Be A Utopian: Matthew Rankin On His New Film 'The Tesla World Light<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i>Cartoon Brew</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">25 May</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Cartoon+Brew&amp;rft.atitle=It%E2%80%99s+Hard+to+Be+A+Utopian%3A+Matthew+Rankin+On+His+New+Film+%27The+Tesla+World+Light%27&amp;rft.date=2017-05-23&amp;rft.aulast=Thrill&amp;rft.aufirst=Scott&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cartoonbrew.com%2Finterviews%2Fhard-utopian-matthew-rankin-new-film-tesla-world-light-150984.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Tesla+World+Light\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.semainedelacritique.com/en/edition/2017/movie/tesla-lumiere-mondiale\">\"TESLA&#160;: LUMI\u00c8RE MONDIALE\"</a>. <i>Semaine de la Critique du Festival de Cannes</i>. Cannes Film Festival.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Semaine+de+la+Critique+du+Festival+de+Cannes&amp;rft.atitle=TESLA+%3A+LUMI%C3%88RE+MONDIALE&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.semainedelacritique.com%2Fen%2Fedition%2F2017%2Fmovie%2Ftesla-lumiere-mondiale&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Tesla+World+Light\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Moreault, \u00c9ric (2017-05-20). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lapresse.ca/le-soleil/arts/dossiers/festival-de-cannes/201705/20/01-5099972-loriginal-de-winnipeg-la-fausse-bombe-de-cannes.php\">\"L'original de Winnipeg, la fausse bombe de Cannes\"</a>. <i>Le Soleil</i> (in French)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-05-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Le+Soleil&amp;rft.atitle=L%27original+de+Winnipeg%2C+la+fausse+bombe+de+Cannes&amp;rft.date=2017-05-20&amp;rft.aulast=Moreault&amp;rft.aufirst=%C3%89ric&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lapresse.ca%2Fle-soleil%2Farts%2Fdossiers%2Ffestival-de-cannes%2F201705%2F20%2F01-5099972-loriginal-de-winnipeg-la-fausse-bombe-de-cannes.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3As